{"tid":1930677,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(突發) 南華早報職員確診 時代廣場辦公室疏散","createTime":"2020-03-17T17:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T18:44:42.000Z","uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b0209b6a595976cb5b1a48ad7fd3053cce8a8f26","tid":1930677,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:05:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>回力鏢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《南早》職員初步確診 同層即疏散 時代廣場辦公室關閉<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎恐有殺入傳媒業界之憂。本報獲悉，英文報章《南華早報》的辦公室，一名女記者晚上初步確診感染武漢肺炎。據了解，該職員於《南華早報》旗下的《Young Post》擔任自由身記者，有指該報管理層接獲消息後，立即要求與該職員同層工作的人士，即日起在家工作。凌晨有時代廣場管理公司職員，為《南早》位於銅鑼灣時代廣場19樓的寫字樓電梯大堂消毒。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，《南早》已向內部職員發通告證實消息，表示該名女記者3月10日至13日，及3月16日，曾在銅鑼灣的辦公室工作，曾使用19樓的休息區，3月13日的「歡樂時光」時段也使用過公司的內部酒吧Black kite。據悉，該酒吧Black kite早前因應員工在家工作而暫停開放一段日子，上周五（13日）才重開。該名女記者隨即在「歡樂時光」時段使用酒吧設施。公司會通知曾與該女記者有密切接觸的同事相關消息。<br />\n<br />\n通告又指，《南早》位於銅鑼灣時代廣場及黃竹坑辦公室即日起關閉至周末（21日)，若有員工需要返回辦公室取物資，只能於今天早上8時至12時前往辦公室，最多只准在辦公室逗留10分鐘。所有香港分區的員工則繼續在家工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/18/010407_5d1d16fadd56434aa09221cb36532e57.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F18%2F010407_5d1d16fadd56434aa09221cb36532e57.jpeg&h=c29f6691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今早凌晨有時代廣場管理公司職員，為南華早報位於19樓的寫字樓電梯大堂消毒。李家傑攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnkknCL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnkknCL.jpg&h=2e5e5bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南華早報位於時代廣場辦公室今（18日）將關閉。李家傑攝<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8VHAXO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8VHAXO.jpg&h=8b5916f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南華早報管理層接獲消息後，立即要求與該職員同層工作的人士，即日起在家工作。李家傑攝"},{"pid":"770602ac0ee9e332555059b16e02c039f34a12d9","tid":1930677,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:06:20.000Z","msg":"有冇外遊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e319cba1600781b1ffa74433c50707387278da6","tid":1930677,"uid":76341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"內部酒吧lets go<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b23d06d379b831f9d05fb6ce4d63530cb69def","tid":1930677,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825c684d0aa2ec998d16b59921cc5cc73402d48c","tid":1930677,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:13:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c145a6b2c85900f4cd82a28cf18029c9e6154a0e","tid":1930677,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T18:44:42.000Z","msg":"爽、間公司有內部酒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}